1. Adding an Endpoint
Access the Wazuh Dashboard.
Navigate to the Add Agent section.
Provide the server address:
Enter the Wazuh public IP address.
Follow the instructions to generate the installation command:
Copy the generated command and execute it on the endpoint's shell. This will download and install the Wazuh agent.
Start the Wazuh service on the endpoint:
Run the following command in the endpoint shell:
cmd
Copy code
net start wazuhsvc
Open the Services application and verify that the "Wazuh Agent" service is running.
